# Plan: Support Share Issue URLs (CLI-T4)

## Problem

When a user passes a Sentry share URL like `https://gibush-kq.sentry.io/share/issue/f1abd515c51346778384ff25dfb341e5/` to `sentry issue view`, the CLI throws:

> Error: Invalid issue format: "https://gibush-kq.sentry.io/share/issue/f1abd515c51346778384ff25dfb341e5/". Missing pr...

Root cause: `parseSentryUrl()` doesn't recognize `/share/issue/` paths → returns `null` → URL falls through to string pattern matching → fails.

## Solution

Thread share URL support through the three-layer pipeline: **URL parsing → argument parsing → issue resolution**.

Two-step resolution: call the public share endpoint to get the numeric group ID, then fetch full details via the authenticated API.

